high_descs: Pick up the glass with fork in the sink.
Bring the glass with fork to the fridge.
Chill the glass with fork in the fridge.
Bring the glass with fork to the sink.
Put the glass with fork in the right cabinet under the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled glass with fork in the right cabinet under the sink.

high_descs: pick up the glass cup from the sink
turn around towards the door and then left towards the refrigerator
put the glass cup in the refrigerator for 5 minutes and take it out
turn around towards the table and then right towards the sink
put the glass cup in the sink
anns.task_desc: place a cold glass cup in the sink

high_descs: Go straight for a step and turn left to locate the sink.
Pick up the cup and fork from the sink.
Turn around and go to the left side corner of the room to the fridge.
Open the fridge and put the items inside, followed by closing the door. Open the door and retrieve the items out again, closing the door when finished.
Turn around and go to the right side of the sink.
Open the bottom cabinet under the sink, and place the fork and cup inside.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and fork to the cabinet.
